summary:
- **Index Removal:** Spartan Resources Limited (SPR) to be removed from S&P/ASX 200 Index.  
- **Reason:** Acquisition by Ramelius Resources Limited (RMS) pending court approval.  
- **Effective Date:** Removal before market open on **July 23, 2025**.  
- **Replacement:** Infratil Limited (IFT) to be added to S&P/ASX 200 on the same date.  

*Omitted non-material details (background on S&P Dow Jones Indices, contact info).*
